### FacultyHub — Faculty API manual tests (VS Code REST Client / compatible)
###
### Prerequisites
### - Dev server: npm run dev
### - DATABASE_URL set; run: npx prisma db push && npm run db:seed
### - Better Auth: sign in (e.g. via /login) and paste the session cookie below, OR
### - Local mock cookie tests: set in .env  ALLOW_MOCK_AUTH=true  then POST /api/auth/mock-login
###
### Replace {{baseUrl}} and {{cookie}} before running.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@cookie = better-auth.session_token=PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

### --- Valid: canonical GET /api/faculty (directory, all authenticated roles) ---
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/faculty?page=1&limit=5
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### --- Valid: GET /api/faculty/:id ---
# @name facultyId
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/faculty
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### (Copy an id from the list response, then:)
# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/faculty/YOUR-FACULTY-UUID
# Cookie: {{cookie}}

### --- Invalid: malformed query (validation 400) ---
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/faculty?page=not-a-number
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### --- Unauthorized: no cookie ---
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/faculty

### --- Forbidden: student on faculty portal route (after logging in as student@...) ---
# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/faculty/dashboard
# Cookie: {{cookie}}

### --- Not found: faculty request detail ---
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/faculty/requests/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### --- Mock login (only if ALLOW_MOCK_AUTH=true) — staff ---
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/mock-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "faculty@university.edu",
  "password": "password123"
}

### --- Mock login — student (directory only) ---
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/mock-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student@university.edu",
  "password": "password123"
}
